Here are some user stories of this program:

I, the user, should be able to get images from others twitter.
I, the user, should be able to grab tweets through timeline.

I, the user, should be able to generate the world cloud of a twitter user.
I, the user, should be able to calculate the frequency of words.
I, the user, should be able to get emotion analysi from Google NLP API output.
I, the user, should be able to caculate some people's attitude to something.
